These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, fuchsia
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, card-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, analyst
1. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the analyst is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Color   | fuchsia     | blue   |
| Hobby         | card-games | photography |
| Job     | engineer | analyst    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
House: victorian, townhouse
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes blood-red is the townhouse house##1
3. the nigerian is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | malaysian     | nigerian |
| Color   | grey | blood-red  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| House     | victorian   | townhouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, havana
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower
2 different games are played: bridge, canasta
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar    | havana     | siglo |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | daffodil    |
| Game         | bridge         | canasta        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

