.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
City: berlin, edinburgh
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee
There 2 different types of food: peach, potato
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| City           | edinburgh | berlin    |
| Beverage   | tea       | coffee |
| Food           | peach         | potato    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

